<div class="container" id="below-the-fold">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12 below-fold">
      <h2 class="headline">We use a combination of Screen Sharing and Live Audio to teach</h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row row-centered">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 ">
      <h3 class="headline">We love Zoom</h3>

      <p class="tailline">This tool allows us to connect a single or multiple Students to an Instructor for our
      live interractive learning sessions where programming concepts are demonstrated in real time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 ">
      <h3 class="headline">Audio Rocks</h3>
      <p class="tailline">When you type to get your job done, typing to talk isn't really an option. For this
      reason we employ Audio Chat (again through Zoom) so everyone can have a lively discussion.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 ">
      <h3 class="headline">Pair Programming</h3>
      <p class="tailline">During both the Private and the Open Sessions you will get to see master level code
      written before your eyes and explained in detail and of course these sessions can be recorded!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

